maneuvers.narrative: Start out going north on Tall Oaks Ct toward Heather Way.
Turn left onto Heather Way.
Turn right onto Brentwood Dr.
Turn left onto Bellefontaine Rd.
Turn right onto Kitridge Rd.
Turn left onto Brandt Pike/OH-201. Continue to follow OH-201.
Turn left onto Stanley Ave.
Merge onto OH-4 S toward Middletown.
Merge onto I-75 S via the exit on the left toward Cincinnati (Crossing into Kentucky).
Merge onto I-71 S via EXIT 173 toward Louisville.
Merge onto I-264 W via EXIT 5 on the left.
Merge onto I-65 S via EXIT 12 toward Nashville (Crossing into Tennessee).
Merge onto I-40 W via EXIT 84B on the left toward Memphis.
Take EXIT 24-25 toward Jackson Miss/Collierville/Millington/I-269/TN-385.
Keep left at the fork in the ramp.
Merge onto I-269 S via the ramp on the left (Crossing into Mississippi).
I-269 S becomes I-69 S/MS-304 W.
Merge onto I-55 S toward Jackson (Crossing into Louisiana).
Merge onto I-12 W via EXIT 29B toward Baton Rouge.
Take the LA-3245/O'Neal Lane exit, EXIT 7.
Keep left to take the O'Neal Lane ramp.
Turn left onto O'Neal Ln/LA-3245. Continue to follow LA-3245.
LA-3245 becomes Oneal Ln.
Turn right onto George Oneal Rd.
Turn left onto Jones Creek Rd.
Turn left onto Tiger Bend Rd.
Turn right onto Antioch Rd.
Turn right onto Profit Ave.
Turn left onto Vice President Dr.
7527 VICE PRESIDENT DR is on the left.
